<br>
I don't think it necessary to get the skill &gt;150...in fact 100 is often sufficient. That level of skill is hardly a burden to reach.<br>
<br>
 If a lot of warriors are reading this thread and laughing, well it is their right to do so. They can play their characters however they wish ....but I hope they at least think about the discussion rather than dismiss the use of bash out of hand. If you know you are facing a ch-ing or gating mob and you are not the MT...consider bringing along a shield just in case. Interrupting casters is best done by other classes, but if they aren't around the job defaults to you whether you like it or not. <p>Gulor Gularin
