<br>
As far as my play style goes its all moot anyway. I use all my skills. Until I hit 51 all my melee and weapon skills were maxxed. Disarm, kick, bandage everything but bash and beg. I'm working hard to max bash, and after many levels of complaining about using the beg &quot;gimmick&quot; i'm training that quickly too. (side note: my beef is that i shouldn't have to beg to stay at the top of the hate list, not that begging doesn't have a noticeable taunt effect). This means I carry a shield all the time and have hotkeys set up to bash. And all the other things I have to do to keep my skills maxxed out at each level. <br>
